PrecisAmendment to the ABANDONMENT OF BRANCH LINES PROHIBITION ORDER NO. 8 which terminates the operation of an 18.5 mile portion of the Canadian Pacific Limited KISBEY SUBDIVISION in Saskatchewan, extending from a point at or near Stoughton to a point at or near Griffin, which no longer carries any rail traffic, effective June 15, 1993.
